commits.sourceNew:
/**
   * Like {@link #commit()}, but takes an additional commit data to be included
   * w/ the commit.
   * 
   * @see #commit()
   * @see #prepareCommit(Map)
   */
  public void commit(Map<String, String> commitData) throws IOException;
